*What is cloud?
ans-The cloud enables anyone with an internet connection to access IT resources on-demand, such as those consumed by cloud-based applications. The basic resources available are compute, storage, and networking, all of which are needed for a business critical application to deliver a full experience.


*Advantages-
1.Scalability-You can add as well as subtract no. of servers.
2.Cost efficient-According to the requirement  we have to pay only for the time when we use cloud,
3.Security-The cloud computing is more secured as it provides private mode for institution so that candidates can use it effectively.
4.Maintainance-The maintainance is handled by AWS so you need not to pay the extra cost for maintainace.
